description: Exceptional loft in the vibrant Fort Point neighborhood directly on the Channel. This spacious 2-bed condominium offers 1,747 SF of living space on the 6th floor of a professionally managed elevator building. With soaring ceilings, in-unit washer/dryer, deeded parking, and private outdoor space offering gorgeous downtown views, this is an exceptional city home. This penthouse unit is highly desirable given its orientation in the building and exceptional skylights and outdoor space. Inquire with the listing agent about the possibility of merging with an adjacent unit. Enjoy a vibrant neighborhood near the Seaport, Waterfront, and Downtown Boston. This stunning brick and beam loft is not to be missed!
